            td Actions theme color. One of <a href="../docs/color-themes.html">default colors</a>
          tr
            th(colspan="3") &lt;FabActions&gt;
          tr
            td theme
            td string
            td Actions theme color. One of <a href="../docs/color-themes.html">default colors</a>
